<td align="center"><b>
<i>Perdita boltoniae</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">&#40;Robertson, 1902&#41;</font></b><br>
<small><i>Perditella boltoniae </i>Robertson, 1902; <i>Perdita chrysopsina </i>Timberlake, 1928; <i>Perdita &#40;Hexaperdita&#41; boltoniae chrysopsina </i>Timberlake, 1928, valid subspecies</small><p>
